OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778868675
OL,3,CManhunt after stabbing leaves man in
OL,4,Chis 60s in critical condition on park
OL,5,Cbench
OL,7,FThey say they were alarmed after a
OL,8,Fmember of the public found him on a
OL,9,Fnearby bench. He remains in critical
OL,10,Fcondition.
OL,12,FPolice officers were joined by West
OL,13,FMidlands Ambulance Service, the
OL,14,FMidlands Air Ambulance and the
OL,15,FNational Police Air Service.
OL,17,FThe police is searching for a man
OL,18,Fdescribed in his mid to late 20s, of
OL,19,Fan average build, wearing dark
OL,20,Fclothing.
